ygData.messageBody:
Well I have lots and lots of questions after my first Planes trip last night,
but before I bother asking things answered 150 times is there any good links
or places with information I can go read... again.

I have read lots of stuff over the last year but now having been there I have
a different set of eyes with which to read with again.

I will say this much it was very anticlimatic for me. It was Hate and I am
going to get stuff for my enchanter and cleric perma partners and as always
will go to the ends of the earth for them, but after 47 levels to get there I
just had the feeling the entire time of "wow all that for this?" It was a
Highpass for high levels, pull and FFA, pull and FFA.

Is Fear like this too? Any guides out there you can point me to would be
appreciated so I can go read again now having been there.

Thanks!

I apologize if you get this multiple times as I am sending it to the 4 class
list servs I am on.
